{"id": "v3_design_fatigue_shaft_keyway_torsion", "instruction": "请识别关键风险并给出可执行的校核路径。", "input": "对象:键槽轴，高应力区；工况：交变扭矩。未提供键槽宽度与根部圆角、材料状态与扭矩载荷谱。", "output": "1. 失效模式：键槽轴在交变扭矩下存在键槽根部应力集中，须按疲劳而非静强度校核。\n2. 校核：算扭转剪应力幅与缺口效应，需键槽宽度与根部圆角、材料疲劳性能与扭矩载荷谱。\n3. 制造：根部留圆角可喷丸以改善表面完整性。\n4. 检测：根部磁粉检测。\n5. 缺失：键槽宽度与根部圆角、材料热处理状态、扭矩载荷谱、目标寿命。\n边界：键槽根部应力集中对应的应力集中系数需依键槽宽度与根部圆角核定；剪切疲劳寿命的结论需要扭矩载荷谱支撑。", "version": "v3", "task_type": "design_fatigue", "domain": "", "subdomain": "", "difficulty": "hard", "language": "zh", "risk_tags": ["fatigue", "stress_concentration", "missing_information", "surface_integrity"], "numeric_claims": [], "requires_tool": false, "requires_rag": false, "split_group": "v3_sg_design_fatigue_shaft_keyway_torsion", "category": "design_fatigue", "sub_category": "shaft_keyway", "evidence": ["键槽根部应力集中"], "conditions": ["载荷谱", "键槽宽度与根部圆角", "材料状态", "寿命目标"], "author": "claude", "source_type": "expert_authored", "source_ref": "", "license": "pending", "review_status": "v3_pending_review", "reviewer": ""}
{"id": "v3_design_fatigue_shaft_spline_torsion", "instruction": "请识别关键风险并给出可执行的校核路径。", "input": "对象:花键轴，高应力区；工况：交变扭矩。未提供模数与齿根圆角、材料状态与扭矩载荷谱。", "output": "1. 失效模式：花键轴在交变扭矩下存在齿根应力集中与齿面磨损，须按疲劳而非静强度校核。\n2. 校核：算扭转剪应力幅与缺口效应，需模数与齿根圆角、材料疲劳性能与扭矩载荷谱。\n3. 制造：齿根圆角表面淬火以改善表面完整性。\n4. 检测：齿根与齿面检测。\n5. 缺失：模数与齿根圆角、材料热处理状态、扭矩载荷谱、目标寿命。\n边界：齿根应力集中与齿面磨损对应的应力集中系数需依模数与齿根圆角核定；剪切疲劳寿命的结论需要扭矩载荷谱支撑。", "version": "v3", "task_type": "design_fatigue", "domain": "", "subdomain": "", "difficulty": "hard", "language": "zh", "risk_tags": ["fatigue", "stress_concentration", "missing_information", "surface_integrity"], "numeric_claims": [], "requires_tool": false, "requires_rag": false, "split_group": "v3_sg_design_fatigue_shaft_spline_torsion", "category": "design_fatigue", "sub_category": "shaft_spline", "evidence": ["齿根应力集中与齿面磨损"], "conditions": ["载荷谱", "模数与齿根圆角", "材料状态", "寿命目标"], "author": "claude", "source_type": "expert_authored", "source_ref": "", "license": "pending", "review_status": "v3_pending_review", "reviewer": ""}
{"id": "v3_design_fatigue_shaft_smooth_combined", "instruction": "请识别关键风险并给出可执行的校核路径。", "input": "对象:光轴，高应力区；工况：弯扭复合。未提供直径与表面质量、材料状态与弯扭载荷谱。", "output": "1. 失效模式：光轴在弯扭复合下存在名义应力为主无显著应力集中源，须按疲劳而非静强度校核。\n2. 校核：按当量应力合成分别评估静强度与疲劳，需直径与表面质量、材料疲劳性能与弯扭载荷谱。\n3. 制造：保证表面质量直线度以改善表面完整性。\n4. 检测：表面与直线度检查。\n5. 缺失：直径与表面质量、材料热处理状态、弯扭载荷谱、目标寿命。\n边界：名义应力为主无显著应力集中源对应的应力集中系数需依直径与表面质量核定；复合疲劳寿命的结论需要弯扭载荷谱支撑。", "version": "v3", "task_type": "design_fatigue", "domain": "", "subdomain": "", "difficulty": "medium", "language": "zh", "risk_tags": ["fatigue", "stress_concentration", "missing_information"], "numeric_claims": [], "requires_tool": false, "requires_rag": false, "split_group": "v3_sg_design_fatigue_shaft_smooth_combined", "category": "design_fatigue", "sub_category": "shaft_smooth", "evidence": ["名义应力为主无显著应力集中源"], "conditions": ["载荷谱", "直径与表面质量", "材料状态", "寿命目标"], "author": "claude", "source_type": "expert_authored", "source_ref": "", "license": "pending", "review_status": "v3_pending_review", "reviewer": ""}
{"id": "v3_design_fatigue_weld_toe", "instruction": "请识别风险并给出校核方向。", "input": "对象:对接焊接接头；请评估其可靠性。", "output": "1. 失效模式：焊趾应力集中与残余拉应力。\n2. 校核方向：结合板厚与焊脚尺寸按相关方法核算。\n3. 制造/检测：焊缝无损检测。\n边界：焊趾应力集中与残余拉应力的判定需依板厚与焊脚尺寸与适用标准(记录标准号/年份/条款)核定，缺数据时不下确定结论。", "version": "v3", "task_type": "design_fatigue", "domain": "", "subdomain": "", "difficulty": "medium", "language": "zh", "risk_tags": ["fatigue", "stress_concentration", "missing_information"], "numeric_claims": [], "requires_tool": false, "requires_rag": false, "split_group": "v3_sg_design_fatigue_weld_toe", "category": "design_fatigue", "sub_category": "weld_toe", "evidence": ["焊趾应力集中与残余拉应力"], "conditions": ["载荷", "板厚与焊脚尺寸", "材料状态", "适用标准"], "author": "claude", "source_type": "expert_authored", "source_ref": "", "license": "pending", "review_status": "v3_pending_review", "reviewer": ""}
{"id": "v3_fault_diagnosis_pump_排查步骤", "instruction": "请根据现象分析可能原因与排查步骤，区分根因与诱因。", "input": "设备:离心泵；现象:流量与扬程下降。重点:排查步骤。", "output": "排查步骤：可能原因包括叶轮磨损/口环间隙大/汽蚀/密封泄漏。排查须以进出口压力与流量等证据闭环，区分需停机检查与可在线监测的情形。\n边界：结论须以进出口压力与流量为证据支撑；具体处置结合泵型与输送介质确定，不得把可能原因写成唯一故障结论。", "version": "v3", "task_type": "fault_diagnosis", "domain": "", "subdomain": "", "difficulty": "medium", "language": "zh", "risk_tags": ["vibration_resonance", "wear_contact_fatigue", "inspection_ndt", "missing_information"], "numeric_claims": [], "requires_tool": false, "requires_rag": false, "split_group": "v3_sg_fault_diagnosis_pump_排查步骤", "category": "fault_diagnosis", "sub_category": "fault_pump", "evidence": ["叶轮磨损/口环间隙大/汽"], "conditions": ["运行参数", "泵型与输送介质", "历史记录", "监测数据"], "author": "claude", "source_type": "expert_authored", "source_ref": "", "license": "pending", "review_status": "v3_pending_review", "reviewer": ""}
{"id": "v3_fault_diagnosis_pump_处置原则", "instruction": "请根据现象分析可能原因与排查步骤，区分根因与诱因。", "input": "设备:离心泵；现象:流量与扬程下降。重点:处置原则。", "output": "处置原则：可能原因包括叶轮磨损/口环间隙大/汽蚀/密封泄漏。排查须以进出口压力与流量等证据闭环，区分需停机检查与可在线监测的情形。\n边界：结论须以进出口压力与流量为证据支撑；具体处置结合泵型与输送介质确定，不得把可能原因写成唯一故障结论。", "version": "v3", "task_type": "fault_diagnosis", "domain": "", "subdomain": "", "difficulty": "medium", "language": "zh", "risk_tags": ["vibration_resonance", "wear_contact_fatigue", "inspection_ndt", "missing_information"], "numeric_claims": [], "requires_tool": false, "requires_rag": false, "split_group": "v3_sg_fault_diagnosis_pump_处置原则", "category": "fault_diagnosis", "sub_category": "fault_pump", "evidence": ["叶轮磨损/口环间隙大/汽"], "conditions": ["运行参数", "泵型与输送介质", "历史记录", "监测数据"], "author": "claude", "source_type": "expert_authored", "source_ref": "", "license": "pending", "review_status": "v3_pending_review", "reviewer": ""}
{"id": "v3_material_heat_treatment_selection_工程边界", "instruction": "请说明材料/热处理分析的要点与所需条件。", "input": "主题:高强度高韧性选材；关注:工程边界。", "output": "工程边界：中碳调质钢调质获强韧匹配，更高要求用表面淬火或渗碳钢；须同时看屈服冲击疲劳与淬透性，不能只看抗拉。\n边界：具体目标性能与截面尺寸需结合材料手册与认证数据确定，硬度与性能参数以材料认证数据为准，不作普适常数。", "version": "v3", "task_type": "material_heat_treatment", "domain": "", "subdomain": "", "difficulty": "medium", "language": "zh", "risk_tags": ["heat_treatment", "surface_integrity", "missing_information"], "numeric_claims": [], "requires_tool": false, "requires_rag": false, "split_group": "v3_sg_material_heat_treatment_selection_工程边界", "category": "material_heat_treatment", "sub_category": "mat_selection", "evidence": ["中碳调质钢调质获强韧匹配"], "conditions": ["材料牌号", "热处理状态", "目标性能与截面尺寸", "材料手册与认证数据"], "author": "claude", "source_type": "expert_authored", "source_ref": "", "license": "pending", "review_status": "v3_pending_review", "reviewer": ""}
{"id": "v3_material_heat_treatment_evidence_要点", "instruction": "请说明材料/热处理分析的要点与所需条件。", "input": "主题:材料性能证据抽取；关注:要点。", "output": "要点：依据给定文献片段抽取性能并保留温度方向工艺等适用条件，不得把条件性实验值泛化为材料常数。\n边界：具体文献片段与材料状态需结合原文 DOI 与适用条件确定，硬度与性能参数以材料认证数据为准，不作普适常数。", "version": "v3", "task_type": "material_heat_treatment", "domain": "", "subdomain": "", "difficulty": "medium", "language": "zh", "risk_tags": ["heat_treatment", "surface_integrity", "missing_information"], "numeric_claims": [], "requires_tool": false, "requires_rag": false, "split_group": "v3_sg_material_heat_treatment_evidence_要点", "category": "material_heat_treatment", "sub_category": "mat_evidence", "evidence": ["依据给定文献片段抽取性能"], "conditions": ["材料牌号", "热处理状态", "文献片段与材料状态", "原文 DOI 与适用条件"], "author": "claude", "source_type": "expert_authored", "source_ref": "", "license": "pending", "review_status": "v3_pending_review", "reviewer": ""}
{"id": "v3_tolerance_measurement_assembly_chain_需要什么信息", "instruction": "请说明该公差/测量/装配问题的分析要点。", "input": "主题:尺寸链计算；问题:需要什么信息。", "output": "需要什么信息：用极值法或统计法求解封闭环，明确增减环与公差分配。\n边界：公差与配合的具体数值需依各组成环公差与封闭环要求并对照尺寸链分析与公差标准核定，不臆造。", "version": "v3", "task_type": "tolerance_measurement_assembly", "domain": "", "subdomain": "", "difficulty": "medium", "language": "zh", "risk_tags": ["assembly_tolerance", "inspection_ndt", "missing_information"], "numeric_claims": [], "requires_tool": false, "requires_rag": false, "split_group": "v3_sg_tolerance_measurement_assembly_chain_需要什", "category": "tolerance_measurement_assembly", "sub_category": "tol_chain", "evidence": ["用极值法或统计法求解封闭"], "conditions": ["功能要求", "工况", "各组成环公差与封闭环要求", "尺寸链分析与公差标准"], "author": "claude", "source_type": "expert_authored", "source_ref": "", "license": "pending", "review_status": "v3_pending_review", "reviewer": ""}
{"id": "v3_tolerance_measurement_assembly_datum_如何分析", "instruction": "请说明该公差/测量/装配问题的分析要点。", "input": "主题:基准选择；问题:如何分析。", "output": "如何分析：设计工艺测量基准应一致，不一致会累积误差。\n边界：公差与配合的具体数值需依功能基准与装配关系并对照形位公差与基准体系标准核定，不臆造。", "version": "v3", "task_type": "tolerance_measurement_assembly", "domain": "", "subdomain": "", "difficulty": "medium", "language": "zh", "risk_tags": ["assembly_tolerance", "inspection_ndt", "missing_information"], "numeric_claims": [], "requires_tool": false, "requires_rag": false, "split_group": "v3_sg_tolerance_measurement_assembly_datum_如何分", "category": "tolerance_measurement_assembly", "sub_category": "tol_datum", "evidence": ["设计工艺测量基准应一致，"], "conditions": ["功能要求", "工况", "功能基准与装配关系", "形位公差与基准体系标准"], "author": "claude", "source_type": "expert_authored", "source_ref": "", "license": "pending", "review_status": "v3_pending_review", "reviewer": ""}
{"id": "v3_standard_evidence_refusal_no_geom_缺什么", "instruction": "信息不足或无依据时，请明确拒绝并说明缺什么及为何不能给。", "input": "问题:未提供尺寸问圆角半径取多少(缺什么)。", "output": "不能给固定数值。圆角半径影响应力集中；补全结构约束与工艺能力后方可校核。\n注意：不得把可能当结论、不得编造数值、不得无依据引用标准。\n边界：涉及结构约束与工艺能力的具体数值须在补全条件后依计算或标准给出；无来源版本时不引用标准编号，不编造固定数值。", "version": "v3", "task_type": "standard_evidence_refusal", "domain": "", "subdomain": "", "difficulty": "hard", "language": "zh", "risk_tags": ["missing_information", "fabricated_value_risk"], "numeric_claims": [], "requires_tool": false, "requires_rag": false, "split_group": "v3_sg_standard_evidence_refusal_no_geom_缺什么", "category": "standard_evidence_refusal", "sub_category": "ref_no_geom", "evidence": ["不能给固定数值。圆角"], "conditions": ["载荷", "材料状态", "结构约束与工艺能力", "标准"], "author": "claude", "source_type": "expert_authored", "source_ref": "", "license": "pending", "review_status": "v3_pending_review", "reviewer": ""}
{"id": "v3_standard_evidence_refusal_no_life_缺什么", "instruction": "信息不足或无依据时，请明确拒绝并说明缺什么及为何不能给。", "input": "问题:缺载荷谱问疲劳寿命(缺什么)。", "output": "不能给寿命数值。疲劳寿命依赖载荷谱与材料疲劳数据；补全载荷谱与疲劳性能数据后方可校核。\n注意：不得把可能当结论、不得编造数值、不得无依据引用标准。\n边界：涉及载荷谱与疲劳性能数据的具体数值须在补全条件后依计算或标准给出；无来源版本时不引用标准编号，不编造固定数值。", "version": "v3", "task_type": "standard_evidence_refusal", "domain": "", "subdomain": "", "difficulty": "hard", "language": "zh", "risk_tags": ["missing_information", "fabricated_value_risk"], "numeric_claims": [], "requires_tool": false, "requires_rag": false, "split_group": "v3_sg_standard_evidence_refusal_no_life_缺什么", "category": "standard_evidence_refusal", "sub_category": "ref_no_life", "evidence": ["不能给寿命数值。疲劳"], "conditions": ["载荷", "材料状态", "载荷谱与疲劳性能数据", "标准"], "author": "claude", "source_type": "expert_authored", "source_ref": "", "license": "pending", "review_status": "v3_pending_review", "reviewer": ""}
{"id": "v3_standard_evidence_refusal_bolt_std_适用性", "instruction": "请说明相关标准及其适用性。", "input": "问题:螺栓连接的标准(适用性)。", "output": "螺栓力学等级与配合可参考 GB/T 3098 系列等，须核对版本与适用范围。\n边界：该标准的适用范围是紧固件机械性能与配合；使用前须核对版本年份与适用条款，不得盲目套用。", "version": "v3", "task_type": "standard_evidence_refusal", "domain": "", "subdomain": "", "difficulty": "medium", "language": "zh", "risk_tags": ["standard_citation"], "numeric_claims": [], "requires_tool": false, "requires_rag": false, "split_group": "v3_sg_standard_evidence_refusal_bolt_std_适用性", "category": "standard_evidence_refusal", "sub_category": "std_bolt_std", "evidence": ["螺栓力学等级与配合可"], "conditions": ["标准版本", "紧固件机械性能与配合", "条款"], "author": "claude", "source_type": "expert_authored", "source_ref": "", "license": "pending", "review_status": "v3_pending_review", "reviewer": ""}
{"id": "v3_engineering_calculation_torsion_已知与公式", "instruction": "请给出完整计算：已知、公式、单位、过程、结果、假设、未考虑因素。", "input": "计算:扭转剪应力；已知:扭矩 T 与轴径 d。给出:已知与公式。", "output": "已知与公式：公式 Wt=πd³/16，τ=T/Wt；实心圆轴纯扭转弹性范围，未计应力集中。\n边界：该计算结果需依实际许用剪应力须查材料标准复核，单位与适用边界须与给定条件一致，不作普适常数。", "version": "v3", "task_type": "engineering_calculation", "domain": "", "subdomain": "", "difficulty": "medium", "language": "zh", "risk_tags": ["static_strength", "fatigue"], "numeric_claims": [], "requires_tool": false, "requires_rag": false, "split_group": "v3_sg_engineering_calculation_torsion_已知与公式", "category": "engineering_calculation", "sub_category": "calc_torsion", "evidence": ["Wt=πd³/16，τ=T/Wt"], "conditions": ["载荷", "几何", "材料性能", "单位"], "author": "claude", "source_type": "expert_authored", "source_ref": "", "license": "pending", "review_status": "v3_pending_review", "reviewer": ""}
{"id": "v3_industrial_safety_pressure", "instruction": "涉及安全时，请先给出隔离停机防护要求，再谈作业。", "input": "场景:压力容器检修作业。", "output": "安全优先：先泄压至零、隔断挂牌、确认无残余压力介质、按规程置换检测，不得带压紧固拆卸。\n边界：安全操作须遵循企业安全规程与适用法规并依泄压规程与介质特性执行，本文不替代安全责任人判断。", "version": "v3", "task_type": "industrial_safety", "domain": "", "subdomain": "", "difficulty": "hard", "language": "zh", "risk_tags": ["safety_critical"], "numeric_claims": [], "requires_tool": false, "requires_rag": false, "split_group": "v3_sg_industrial_safety_pressure", "category": "industrial_safety", "sub_category": "safety_pressure", "evidence": ["先泄压至零、隔断挂牌、确"], "conditions": ["设备状态", "泄压规程与介质特性", "安全规程"], "author": "claude", "source_type": "expert_authored", "source_ref": "", "license": "pending", "review_status": "v3_pending_review", "reviewer": ""}
